milestones.description: Vettori and Kyle Mills's 70-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 68 between Vettori and McCullum

stories.title: Aussies hold nerve for 17-run win

stories.summary: Australia narrowly survived hurricanes from Chris Cairns and Kyle Mills and another terrible middle-order collapse to draw level in the Chappell-Hadlee Series at Sydney
